category: Libs
requires: libode1 libstdc++6-devel
external-source: ode
sdesc: "Open Dynamics Engine library (development)"
ldesc: "ODE is a free, industrial quality library for simulating 
articulated rigid body dynamics - for example ground vehicles, legged 
creatures, and moving objects in VR environments. It is fast, flexible, 
robust and platform independent, with advanced joints, contact with 
friction, and built-in collision detection."
